              %p.mt5 We provide staff for half marathons, world championships, COVID testing centres, beer tents, music concerts, Lapland, promotional tours and in a hundred other situations. We like to say that we’re only as good as our workers, but if we put all modesty aside for a second, we think our management team is pretty incredible at keeping everything running smoothly, too.
